 man\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 152}, {\"ngram\": \"the chocolate muffins\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen's posts, highlighting his adoration of the fudgy morsels, drewmillions of viewsas he competed at the Paris Olympics and led to numerous duplicate muffin recipes (including one inThe New York Times).\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999762444535, \"rank\": 2.330172073151586e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christiansen's posts\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"his adoration\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"the fudgy morsels\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"drewmillions\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"viewsas\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous duplicate muffin recipes\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement But one New York City-based fan of Christiansen's posts did not want to settle for only a reproduction.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999762444535, \"rank\": 2.330172073151586e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christiansen's posts\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"only a reproduction\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Kelin Carolyn Zhang, a 32-year-old independent designer, wondered if she could try the real deal.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"score\": 0.9725338307333412, \"rank\": 0.025795861713158806, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 32-year-old independent designer\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the real deal\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was an initial hurdle, however, since the supplier of the famed Olympic chocolate muffins, Coup de Pates, completes only wholesale orders such as those placed by restaurants and businesses rather than direct-to-consumer, she said.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an initial hurdle\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the supplier\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"the famed Olympic chocolate muffins\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"Coup de Pates\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"only wholesale orders\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"businesses\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she attempted to obtain the authentic muffins, Zhang documented her research and her quest to bring them statesideon TikTok, leading to a connection in the restaurant industry that helped make her wish possible.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1039, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.967569079104443e-39, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the authentic muffins\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"her research\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"her quest\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"a connection\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"the restaurant industry\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"her wish\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The entire situation just kept escalating, and I found it incredibly hilarious, and so I kept going,\\\" Zhang said.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The entire situation\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"extremely random rabbit hole\\\" of muffin research, as she described it, eventually resulted in a shipment of 13 cases containing 300 of the chocolate muffins - presumably the same ones served to athletes at theOlympicsand Paralympics, though Coup de Pates did not respond to requests for comment on the topic.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\\"extremely random rabbit hole\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"muffin research\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"a shipment\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"13 cases\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"the chocolate muffins\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"presumably the same ones\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsand Paralympics\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"Coup de Pates\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"requests\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"comment\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the topic\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The muffins were air-freighted overnight on dry ice on a flight from Paris Orly Airport to Newark Liberty International Airport in New Jersey, Zhang said.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newark_Liberty_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7471046997083895e-14, \"text\": \"Newark Liberty International Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newark_Liberty_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newark_Liberty_International_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.9999999630495047, \"rank\": 3.692147974071205e-08, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The muffins\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"dry ice\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"a flight\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"Orly Airport\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shipment required FDA approval, and the muffins had to clear customs before they were transported by van to the New York cafeIsshiki Matchain the East Village, where the first pop-up event was held Aug. 17.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.44540147423843e-31, \"text\": \"FDA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\"}, {\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999762444535, \"rank\": 2.330172073151586e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\", \"score\": 0.9968205661580373, \"rank\": 0.0010645904504647525, \"text\": \"East Village\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shipment\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"customs\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"van\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"Matchain\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"the first pop-up event\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the event was announced, something of alocal frenzy ensued.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1971}, {\"ngram\": \"alocal frenzy\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thefirst customerlined up outside the cafe at 6 a.m. - the event started four hours later.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thefirst\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the cafe\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"6 a.m.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The line wrapped around the block twice, and the muffins - limited to one per customer for $10 - sold out in roughly two hours, according to Isshiki Matcha owner Angel Zheng, who said her friends who arrived late did not get one.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 231