ore\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.7317326886753523e-11, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang's TikTok posts\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"the two women\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just really like side quests,\\\" Zheng said.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9978068370693186, \"rank\": 0.0011642126938187017, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"side quests\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I like doing things for the plot.\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the plot\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very young - I am 24.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not a big corporation.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big corporation\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not have a boss with a 20-person chain of command.\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a boss\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"a 20-person chain\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"command\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I open restaurants and it brings so much joy to people.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"so much joy\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I was like, if it works, it works.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if it does not, at least we tried.\\\"\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pulling off the event was no small feat, as the process included many logistical hurdles, which Zhangrecounted in detail on X.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"no small feat\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"many logistical hurdles\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"detail\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"X.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coup de Pates had never exported to New York before, so there was no system in place to get the goods from the plane to the restaurant, as Zheng was used to with other suppliers, meaning she and Zhang had to coordinate ground transportation.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2985, \"end\": 2993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999762444535, \"rank\": 2.330172073151586e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 3088, \"end\": 3093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9978068370693186, \"rank\": 0.0011642126938187017, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qi